      <title>加拿大 Mach 公司正在洽谈拯救电动巴士制造商 Lion</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/canada-s-mach-in-talks-to-help-rescue-electric-bus-maker-lion-electric</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，加拿大房地产开发商 Groupe Mach Inc. 的投资部门 Mach Capital 正在讨论向资金短缺的电动巴士制造商 Lion Electric Co. 提供更多资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/canada-s-mach-in-talks-to-help-rescue-electric-bus-maker-lion-electric</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 18:47:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Jane Street 称前交易员在加入 Millennium 之前曾嘲笑过该公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/jane-street-says-ex-trader-mocked-dumb-millennium-strategies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[简街集团 (Jane Street Group) 称，一名前交易员曾嘲笑其新雇主的策略“愚蠢”，该交易员声称此人为千禧年管理公司 (Millennium Management) 窃取了价值数十亿美元的印度期权秘密策略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/jane-street-says-ex-trader-mocked-dumb-millennium-strategies</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 18:07:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃莱克特拉股价暴跌，萨利纳斯一天将损失 50 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/salinas-set-to-lose-4-billion-in-a-day-as-elektra-slumps-60</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在监管机构下令交易所在停牌数月后恢复交易后，Grupo Elektra 股价周一暴跌 67%，亿万富翁里卡多·萨利纳斯·普利戈 (Ricardo Salinas Pliego) 的财富因此蒸发近 50 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/salinas-set-to-lose-4-billion-in-a-day-as-elektra-slumps-60</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 15:43:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油价格持稳，因 OPEC 不确定性抵消中国经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走强，且市场担心 OPEC+ 不会推迟增产，油价企稳，削弱了中国经济逐步复苏的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 23:28:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2024 年最后一个月股市开盘创历史新高：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/asian-stocks-poised-for-gains-after-best-us-month-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大科技公司的股价上涨，推动股市创下历史新高，交易员们正准备迎接一系列经济数据和美联储发言人的讲话，这些数据和讲话将有助于决定利率前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/asian-stocks-poised-for-gains-after-best-us-month-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 22:44:11 GMT</pubDate>
